<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3361] &quot;maxNumberOfBackups&quot; does not work with &quot;backupAfter&quot;=commit</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3361</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Tom&#225;s Fern&#225;ndez L&#246;bbe reported on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3033&quot; title=&quot;&amp;quot;numberToKeep&amp;quot; on replication handler does not work with &amp;quot;backupAfter&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-3033&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-3033&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; that when specifying the init parameter combination &quot;maxNumberOfBackups&quot; with &quot;backupAfter&quot;=commit, the backups do not get cleaned up.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
